{
  "stem": "11133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, my hair had just started growing out, and I was skinny as anything, and I looked awful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, like a skeleton, practically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that's how I remember my birthday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, I also realized that I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had-- I didn't know how to write.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I knew how to read, because one of the things I forgot to tell you was that in Plaszow, they brought books from all over to burn them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the women who were in charge of burning the books used to steal them-- under penalty of death-- hide them on them, bring them back to the barracks, and pass them around to read at night, you know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we would just-- so we read, you know, by the night light.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I knew how to read, but I didn't know how to write.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had lost-- you know, I was 14, and I only had two years of school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So the important thing was to get caught up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started learning as quickly as possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents got me a tutor, and I tried to cram in as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was this in Krakow?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got there, as I said, in May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the summer to do it in, because I was trying to make it into school in September.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took the exams, and I made it into the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I made up six years of school in one summer, and made it into-- there was only two Jewish girls were accepted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, in September, there was another pogrom in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
